{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"60c84ca248","title":"在中央军委扩大会议上的讲话提纲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"591c87c6b8","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":11,"articleId":"60c84ca248"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b5ba322fbc","type":"title","text":"在中央军委扩大会议上的讲话提纲","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"655dbdd91f","type":"paragraph","text":"会开得好。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"182dfb1047","type":"paragraph","text":"起心不良，走到反面","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"626a79e9ad","type":"paragraph","text":"从来就不是一个马克思主义者，只是一个同路人。要论这一点材料是充分的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"4386043deb","type":"paragraph","text":"彭德怀不如孙中山。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"848b5af670","type":"paragraph","text":"高彭都是“军觉论”，彭的“小资产阶级「阶级]狂热性”“得不偿失论”“人民公社搞槽了”“阶级关【系】紧张”“反“左”比反右难”“无产阶级专政官主义最多”等等，难道有一点点马克思主义气味吗？","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"6627d55663","type":"paragraph","text":"同路人不可能不犯错误。借彭黄教育广大群众。大多数善良人能进入共产主义。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"73b2d9458a","type":"paragraph","text":"五次路线错误，极其严重","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"5aa5ace956","type":"paragraph","text":"阴谋分裂活动，违反铁的纪律，破坏无产阶级专政","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"42164bab2d","type":"paragraph","text":"团结旗帜的必要。为全民族在几个五年内建成强大国家，必需铁的纪律，必须团结起来。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"2a058f6df3","type":"paragraph","text":"形势极为有利。一个月月】内，形势大变","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"8bf49d4d2b","type":"paragraph","text":"总路线，大跃进，人民公社，确是真理。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"5be4d2d905","type":"paragraph","text":"军队的任务。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"60052c9617","type":"paragraph","text":"国际的团结。一定要同苏联同志搞好，一定可以搞好的。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"888cd9a22b","type":"paragraph","text":"切不可以背着祖国，里通外国。自古以来，理（里》通外国的人，从来没有好结果。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"8616387a68","type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎彭德怀同志的觉悟。我们大家都要帮助他（其他人也一样）。我相信，他会改好的，只要他肯改，我们肯帮。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"d8aa817d6d","type":"paragraph","text":"他把95%的同志的政治觉悟，低估了，把他自己的能力、威望，高估了。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"628064899b","type":"paragraph","text":"他不是一个马克思【主义】者，而是民主革命的同路人。他肯改，我们肯帮，一定会学好马克思主义的。孔子日：“假我数年，卒以学易，可以无大过。”学哲学（宇宙观，方法论）极为重要。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"f95fbb55cd","type":"paragraph","text":"要准备听几年闲话；要诚息待人，不讲假话；要靠拢大多数如此就一定可以变过来。否则不能。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"3e2e8f5381","type":"paragraph","text":"“人非圣人，熟能无过。”“君子之过也，如日月之蚀意。过也，人皆见之。改也，人皆仰之。”","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"ea25c86f94","type":"paragraph","text":"我也是一个甚为不足的人。很有些时候，我自己不欢喜我自已。马克思主义各部门学问，没有学好。外国文，没有学通。经济工作，刚刚开始学。但我决心学，不死不休。对于这些，我也要改，要进取。那时，见马克思的时候，我的心情就会舒畅一些了。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"4a98318d23","type":"paragraph","text":"我学会了游水。一有意志，万事皆成。我劝同志们也和我一道学习。事务太多，时间不足，然亦可以挤一点。养成学的习惯，就能学下去。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"43cbd70bef","type":"paragraph","text":"我们战胜地球，建立强国，一定要如此，一定要如此。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"},{"id":"2828e18fd9","type":"paragraph","text":"全党全民团结起来，全世界无产者团结起来，目的一定可以以】达到。","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248"}],"page":{"id":"ece60a7456","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"60c84ca248","start":360,"end":361}}}},"__N_SSG":true}